  "time_ut": 1656827455,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d9c\u0dda \u0dc5\u0d9f \u0db1\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dcf \u0dad\u0dd2\u0db6\u0dd6 \u0dba\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0db4\u0dd0\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dca \u0db4\u0dd9\u0da7\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dbd\u0dca \u0d85\u0daf\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0dc4\u0daf\u0dbd\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "They tried to draw petrol from the motorcycle parked near the house",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The attempt of a person who came to steal fuel from a motorcycle parked in front of a house in Buttala Yudhganawa Colony failed when the owner of the house saw it.",
        "At around eight o'clock in the night, a businessman in Buttala city saw a small bucket hanging from the motorcycle parked in front of his house. While checking it, he saw that the pipe of the fuel tank had been taken off and it was prepared to fill with fuel.",
        "Immediately after looking around in this regard with the residents, a person was seen running away from the wall and a can and a pipe were found on the side of the wall with a can and a pipe to fill the pair of sandals he had brought.",
        "The home owner has also lodged a complaint with the Buttala police station regarding the incident."
      ],
